{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","roleHeading":"Structure","symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"title":"OUDSRadio","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"See ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","text":"Orange Business Tool